         <abstract>
            <p>In this paper a sufficient condition for the uniqueness of best $L_2[0, 1]$ approximation by piecewise polynomials of order $k$ with variable breakpoints is generalized from that of order 2. Other extensions included here are nonuniqueness and eventual uniqueness results.</p>
          </abstract>
